tracks.global_prompt: Imagine a sun-drenched afternoon where catchy melodies dance like golden rays through the air, set to an infectious 112 BPM pulse that invites you to sway with a light-hearted chill. Layered with radiant guitars and shimmering synths, this pop song in F# unfolds like a gentle breeze, effortlessly blending uplifting harmonies as it guides you into a blissful state of euphoria.
